originalText.text: I had a great experience at this parking garage. I’ve used dozens of garages all over the city and they all have their issues. I had no issues at all here. Immediate drop off and pickup within 2 minutes of paying. Attendants were super polite, courteous, and took great care of my car. I would recommend this facility if you need to park in midtown, and the price was great too! Check the app or website for coupons.

originalText.text: I am giving this parking garage three starts due to how well their staff treat their customers.  Great service and they do not cheat you; although their prices are too heigh.  The main reason for my low rating is due to their $20 fee for what they refer to as oversized vehicles.  In my case, I drive an Avalanche and it registers fine through all the size measurements.  If that’s the case, then why the extra charge? I can see if the vehicle was a large van that did not fit through the garage, but a regular size SUV/TRUCK that fits in a parking space should not be subjected to these extra charges.  The worse part of it is that all the parking areas in NY are combined on this charge and all will charge you the same.  I wanted to go to Time Sqaure for a very short time to take pictures and I was fine with the $40 charge, but the addition of the $20 oversize charge made it $60 and that’s too much to pay for a one or two hour visit.

originalText.text: This was my second time driving to NY. Reserved parking using BestParking App with a nice discount. I picked up 5 days later about 30 minutes after I said I would. Car was down and ready in under 5 minutes. They honored the discount code without fuss. Quick service. Prime location. Great discount. 5 stars doesn't do this transaction justice.

originalText.text: Have been parking in icon garages for all these years and they are not the cheapest places to park but worth the safety. However, this garage was a horrible one. We unfortunately had to deal with the same attendant while coming in and leaving. On top of his ignorant behavior, he drove our vehicle screeching in the parking garage. He was aweful. The only job he had was to park the car or bring it out and he couldn't even do that decently.
